# Chuan hoa ket thuc dong (line endings).
#
# Vi sao can file nay: repo co ca script Linux (may-in-lbp2900.sh) lan script
# Windows (cai-may-in-lbp2900-windows.bat/.ps1), nen nguoi dung rat de clone
# tren Windows roi chep sang may Linux. Neu khong co file nay, Git tren Windows
# (core.autocrlf=true) se ghi ra ban CRLF, va bash tren Linux se bao loi rat kho
# hieu, vi du:
#     may-in-lbp2900.sh: line 49: $'\r': command not found
#     may-in-lbp2900.sh: line 131: syntax error near unexpected token `$'do\r''
# Cac file nguon C bi CRLF thi van build duoc, nhung tarball hoac patch bi CRLF
# thi hong han (da gap thuc te 2026-07-22: tarball dong goi tu Windows lam
# configure chet voi "config.status: error: cannot find input file: Makefile.in"
# du file do van nam day).

# Mac dinh: de Git tu nhan dien van ban, nhung KHONG tu doi kieu ket thuc dong.
* -text

# Cac file BAT BUOC phai la LF vi chi chay tren Linux
*.sh          text eol=lf
*.c           text eol=lf
*.h           text eol=lf
*.patch       text eol=lf
*.ppd         text eol=lf
Makefile*     text eol=lf
configure*    text eol=lf

# Cac file chay tren Windows: giu CRLF
*.bat         text eol=crlf
*.ps1         text eol=crlf

# File nhi phan: tuyet doi khong dung toi
*.tar.gz      binary
*.tgz         binary
*.zip         binary
*.pcapng      binary
*.pdf         binary
*.png         binary
*.jpg         binary
